{
  "text": "At four downstream locations for the two near wall sources, normalised diffusivity values are shown in Fig. 21 for y \u2264 2\u03c3 . The discontinuity observed in some of the LES profiles in Fig. 21 is near the region where the mean concentration gradient is zero. The diffusivity values from Eq. 5 are compared with those estimated from the DNS data [CITATION_1] using the equation",
