    "124966644": {
      "title": "Direct numerical simulation of turbulent channel flow up to Re = 590",
      "abstract": "Numerical simulations of fully developed turbulent channel flow at three Reynolds numbers up to Re\u03c4=590 are reported. It is noted that the higher Reynolds number simulations exhibit fewer low Reynolds number effects than previous simulations at Re\u03c4=180. A comprehensive set of statistics gathered from the simulations is available on the web at http://www.tam.uiuc.edu/Faculty/Moser/channel."
    }
  }
